title: Which Country Artists RSVP’d 'No' To Bobby's Wedding? + Awkward Prom Stories + Can A 14 Year-Old Get Their Nose Pierced?
itunes:title: Which Country Artists RSVP’d 'No' To Bobby's Wedding? + Awkward Prom Stories + Can A 14 Year-Old Get Their Nose Pierced?
description:
Bobby gives us a wedding update and which artists can’t make it because they're back to playing concerts. It’s prom season! So, we all share awkward prom stories from back in our high school days. Plus, Bobby reads an email from a listener whose 14-year-old is begging them to get their nose pierced and wants to know what we think about it.
